CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Ategrity Specialty is a profitable and growing specialty insurance company dedicated to providing excess and surplus ("E&S") products to small to medium-sized businesses ("SMBs") across the United States. We have built a proprietary underwriting platform that combines sophisticated data analytics with automated and streamlined processes to efficiently serve our clients and deliver long-term value to our stockholders. Our strong value proposition has contributed to a growing network of 460 distribution partners as of December 31, 2024. Currently, the verticals that we focus on are Real Estate, Hospitality, Construction, and Retail.
